welcome_message_body: "Welcome to West St. Paul, where charm and hospitality await you! Immerse yourself in our city's vibrant culture, rich history, and stunning scenery. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that West St. Paul has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Downtown Airport serves domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Downtown Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free WiFi throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Minneapolis - St. Paul International Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at Minneapolis - St. Paul International Airport, primarily serving low-cost carriers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Flying Cloud Airport serves all commercial flights and includes amenities such as restaurants, shops, and rental car services.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Flying Cloud Airport caters to private and charter flights, offering a luxurious lounge and concierge services.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport and is free for all passengers.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Crystal Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Crystal Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Anoka County-Blaine Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Anoka County-Blaine Airport caters to private and corporate flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
